  "text": "where α (n) = w T (n)i v (n)i and v (n)i stands for the transpose of the i-th row of cofactors of the matrix A (n) extended with a zero in the last dimension. Note that w (n)i has to be computed iteratively, thus matrices A (n) and b (n) have to be correctly initialized first. For further details see [CITATION_1] .",
